  "title": "Urgent Hiring: Temp Retail Runner | $14/hr | Orchard | 4-5 days work week",
  "description": "<p>Urgent Hiring: Temp Retail Runner | $14/hr | Orchard |4-5 days work week </p><p>We are urgently looking for a Temp Retail Runner to support daily store operations. We are seeking candidates with strong punctuality, a positive attitude, and reliability.</p><p><strong>🕒 Details</strong></p><ul><li>Salary: $14 per hour</li><li>Duration: Now till mid-February</li><li>Working Days: 4–5 days per week</li><li>Working Hours: Rostered by Supervisor, Min 6 hours per day</li></ul><p><strong>👟 Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Support store operations and daily retail activities</li><li>Assist retail staff with ad-hoc operational tasks</li><li>Ensure smooth flow of stock and in-store support</li><li>Maintain store efficiency during peak hours</li></ul><p>✅ <strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Prior experience in a fast-paced retail environment</li><li>Retail experience preferred</li><li>Independent, proactive, and able to take initiative</li><li>Reliable, punctual, and with a good working attitude</li></ul><p><strong>📩 Interested? Apply Now!</strong></p><p>Send your resume in <strong>MS Word format to: Vanessa.chua@crew.sg</strong></p><p>Please include your <strong>availability, notice period, and expected salary.</strong></p><p><em>* Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</em></p><p>Vanessa Chua Peng Teng (R25158315)</p><p>HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd - CREW by HRnet</p><p>E.A. 24C2435</p>",
